        "message": "=Hi {{ $json.firstName }}, \n\nThank you so much for shopping with Alpha Digital Store!\nWe have successfully received your order.  \n\nBecause your order total is ${{ $json.orderTotal }}, you have officially been unlocked as one of our VIP customers! 🌟  \n\nAs a token of our appreciation, here is an exclusive 20% discount code for your next purchase: 👉 Your Discount Code: VIP20  \n\nWe are already preparing your package for immediate shipping to {{ $json.country }}, and we will update you with the tracking details very soon.  \n\nThank you for choosing us, and have a wonderful day!  \n\nBest regards, \nAlpha Digital Store Team",
